==Описание==

The [[Image:Assembly_ImportMulti.svg‎‎|24px]] [[Assembly3_ImportMultiDocument|Import as multi-document]] command opens a file browser window to search and select STEP files.

STEP assemblies are imported into separate documents.

== Применение ==

# Press {{Button|[[Image:Assembly_ImportMulti.svg‎‎|16px]] [[Assembly3_ImportMultiDocument|Import as multi-document]]}} to open a file browser window
# Select the STEP file to import


